  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras/574093329008416f79da138bbb52391f.avif?t=1749697853\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras_big/574093329008416f79da138bbb52391f.avif?t=1749697853 width=800 height=285 /></span><strong><i> <br> </i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><br>   </i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Laser Tag Massacre </i></strong>is a narrative-driven survival horror game inspired by 80s slasher movies, featuring a retro PS1-style aesthetic.  <br> <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras/2ab0210aa06f081d4891956b8cb158d4.poster.avif?t=1749697853\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras/2ab0210aa06f081d4891956b8cb158d4.webm?t=1749697853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras/2ab0210aa06f081d4891956b8cb158d4.mp4?t=1749697853\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>A Deadly Game Begins...</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On Halloween night, five friends throw a party in an abandoned arcade deep in rural Campinas, Brazil. What starts as a fun night of laser tag quickly turns into a fight for survival.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras/04c6f8be6d75284031c0bc59ec61a455.poster.avif?t=1749697853\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras/04c6f8be6d75284031c0bc59ec61a455.webm?t=1749697853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras/04c6f8be6d75284031c0bc59ec61a455.mp4?t=1749697853\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Variety of Mini-Games...</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While the horror builds, enjoy a variety of fun mini-games scattered throughout the arcade :) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras/ef71a5016eef20d0ed419294555b6370.poster.avif?t=1749697853\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras/ef71a5016eef20d0ed419294555b6370.webm?t=1749697853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras/ef71a5016eef20d0ed419294555b6370.mp4?t=1749697853\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Will You Survive?</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the arcade, play mini-games, but remember: the real horror is never far away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras/70cde897e9394ee3ea376e32f3fdd9b4.poster.avif?t=1749697853\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras/70cde897e9394ee3ea376e32f3fdd9b4.webm?t=1749697853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras/70cde897e9394ee3ea376e32f3fdd9b4.mp4?t=1749697853\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras/574093329008416f79da138bbb52391f.avif?t=1749697853\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras_big/574093329008416f79da138bbb52391f.avif?t=1749697853 width=800 height=285 /></span><strong><i> <br> </i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><br>   </i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Laser Tag Massacre </i></strong>is a narrative-driven survival horror game inspired by 80s slasher movies, featuring a retro PS1-style aesthetic.  <br> <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras/2ab0210aa06f081d4891956b8cb158d4.poster.avif?t=1749697853\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras/2ab0210aa06f081d4891956b8cb158d4.webm?t=1749697853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras/2ab0210aa06f081d4891956b8cb158d4.mp4?t=1749697853\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>A Deadly Game Begins...</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On Halloween night, five friends throw a party in an abandoned arcade deep in rural Campinas, Brazil. What starts as a fun night of laser tag quickly turns into a fight for survival.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras/04c6f8be6d75284031c0bc59ec61a455.poster.avif?t=1749697853\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras/04c6f8be6d75284031c0bc59ec61a455.webm?t=1749697853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras/04c6f8be6d75284031c0bc59ec61a455.mp4?t=1749697853\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Variety of Mini-Games...</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While the horror builds, enjoy a variety of fun mini-games scattered throughout the arcade :) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras/ef71a5016eef20d0ed419294555b6370.poster.avif?t=1749697853\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras/ef71a5016eef20d0ed419294555b6370.webm?t=1749697853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras/ef71a5016eef20d0ed419294555b6370.mp4?t=1749697853\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Will You Survive?</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the arcade, play mini-games, but remember: the real horror is never far away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras/70cde897e9394ee3ea376e32f3fdd9b4.poster.avif?t=1749697853\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras/70cde897e9394ee3ea376e32f3fdd9b4.webm?t=1749697853\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3579960/extras/70cde897e9394ee3ea376e32f3fdd9b4.mp4?t=174969